Description
-----------

The **r\_showShadowCount** cvar provides diagnostic information by
colouring pixels based on the number of shadow volumes calculated for
that pixel. The colours used are the same as those given by
**[r\_showLightCount](R_showLightCount_%28cvar%29 "R showLightCount (cvar)")**
, although the shadow-count is per-pixel rather than per-poly.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_showShadowCount [int]

Parameters
----------

-   [int]
    -   0 - Disable.
    -   1 - Enable.

