Notes
-----

This CVar is the used similarly to **r\_showLightCount** for
optimisation purposes. Excessive shadow volumes can cause a drop in
performance, while an even greater excess causes ugly rendering
artefacts caused by overflow in the stencil buffer. Shadow count can be
reduced by

-   disabling shadow-casting on some lights
-   adding the key **noshadows** with value **1** to
    [func\_statics](Func_static "Func static")
-   reducing polycount, such as by subdividing [patches](Patch "Patch")
    .

